---

<style>

@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Zen+Kaku+Gothic+Antique&display=swap');

*{
 
  font-family: "Zen Kaku Gothic Antique", sans-serif;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-style: normal;
}
  
 body{
  background: #F8F8F8;
 }
  .cont{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 30px;
    height: 90vh;
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 15px;
    
    
  }
    
    .left-section {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #4C44D7 0%, #d2d2d2 100%);
      color: white;
      height: 80%;
      width: 30%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
    }
    .right-section {
      width: 50%;
      height: 80%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      border-radius: 15px;
    }
    .logo {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      height: 100px;
    }



    .title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .form input {
      width: 300px;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .form button {
      width: 320px;
      padding: 1rem;
      background-color: black;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .form a {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      color: #000;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .form a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #888;
    }
  </style>
 
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cont">
    <div class="left-section">
      <h1 class="title">PUP</h1>
      <img src="public/img/Logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo" />
      <p> Con la colaboración y el compromiso de todos,
         podremos alcanzar objetivos 
        y asegurar un crecimiento sostenible y rentable para nuestra organización.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="right-section">
      <h2>Iniciar sesión</h2>
      <form class="form">
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Correo" required />
        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Contraseña" required />
        <a href="/dashboard"><button type="button">Iniciar sesión</button></a>
        <a href="/register">Registrarse</a>
      </form>
      <p class="footer">Copyright 2024 - 2025 Sena</p>
   </div>
  </div>
  </div>
  